  "detail": {
    "tagExpireTime": "1756449942503",
    "endLabelIds": "",
    "endLabelNames": "",
    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1274706583716237312",
    "content": "<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">尊敬的商家：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">您好，为适应业务发展要求，现需对《京东开放平台个人/个体合规管理规则》进行调整</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">，现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年8月22日- 2025年8月28日，规则预计于2025年8月29日生效，公示期满后平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">原规则链接</strong>：<a href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=923540006109319168\">https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=923540006109319168</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">核心调整点</strong>：对恶意占库存的范围进行调整，增加多次或多量超出非自用需求下单但不收货的形式。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">调整内容如下：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: white;\">29、【恶意占库存】</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 21pt; background-color: white; font-family: 宋体;\"><span class=\"15\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">29.1</span></span><span class=\"15\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">【违规情形】</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家在平台多次或多量超出非自用需求下单但不付款<span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">或不收货的形式干扰消费者购物权益或其他商家权益，损害平台正常经营秩序的行为。</span></span></p>",
